Dear Maker Community,

All files in this package were created by myself. YOu'll find a list of all resources which need other credits than me in this file:

InquiVX folder: edits of TheInquisitors XP files for VX resolution - YOu need to give TheInquisitor Credits if you use them.

Misc_Stuff:
"temple parallax" based on the VX RTP
"höhleneingang" (cave entry) "stuhl gekippt" (chairs tilted) based on the VX_Mack set.

Antique Interior set: some tiles are based on Squares Seiken Densetsu 3, but more than 50% are completely new ones. All tiles were made from scratch. The colors are exactly overtaken.

"fette_tuer" was made and animated by "therofler", frame and bottom are from myself

All chibi-sized tiles and the exterior wood set were completely made by myself, but I have to say that I used internet references for the sail symbols. 

If you use stuff from other co-autors you must give them credits.
If you want to use my for non-commercial games you just have to credit me (Cyangmou)
 
If you want to use graphics for a commercial game , write me a mail:
cyangmou.deviantart.com
http://www.pixeljoint.com/p/32234.htm

have fun with the maker!
Cyangmou

